span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"35859f3541ba91c64875cf91282b29134b9a2988","tid":492672,"uid":62815,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T23:52:14.000Z","msg":"港乜撚嘢產<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d8981761e165fa33b6f3aba81ed9025570860bb","tid":492672,"uid":16904,"like":22,"dislike":4,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T23:57:00.000Z","msg":"國際麵包大師PETER YUEN課程〈三〉手擀酥皮實戰班<br />\n日期：12月12日(二)<br />\n時間：1pm-4:40pm<br />\n課程內容：雙色朱古力牛角包/Peter招牌牛角包/豹紋酥皮<br />\n學費：$1,380/位 <br />\n<br />\n國際麵包大師PETER YUEN課程〈一〉歐式早餐麵包<br />\n日期：12月11日(一)<br />\n時間：11am-5pm<br />\n學費：1,780/位<br />\n<br />\n查詢：<br />\nDOLCE DOLCE KITCHEN &amp; GOURMET<br />\n地址：觀塘成業街6號泓富廣場9樓906-907室<br />\n電話： 2151 0609<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n到最後咪又係廣告😂😂"},{"pid":"902e77799d9a9db3ea862a996d1588e8a1e3c611","tid":492672,"uid":28151,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T00:06:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>美籍 代表美國出賽 同港產有咩關係?</blockquote><br />\n就咁睇內文 八歳移民 如果係咁嘅話叫港產真係冇錯啵。分分鐘仲有香港身份證(如果仲拎住張身份證，又冇renounce中國藉，佢仲會首先係一個中國人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)。香港人身份不嬲同國藉冇關架啦<br />\n不過報紙佬拎人個岀生打飛機，又唔問下人老豆教佢嘅同外國人造嘅方法有咩唔同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9bf5da5c6716b49d6293c5afa1f052a02c3f95f","tid":492672,"uid":40932,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T00:10:31.000Z","msg":"笑左計dna<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁認親認戚同支那狗有咩分別<br />\n香港留唔住人才就計dna<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁有香港居留權既外藉人士都唔係香港人啦"},{"pid":"07f8dcfc595a957c3834b6ce3dc8b418d7b20cdd","tid":492672,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T00:11:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咪認親認戚啦"},{"pid":"7540c7ab662263aae26bfc8c32ae941a299df6eb","tid":492672,"uid":40932,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T00:11:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>美籍 代表美國出賽 同港產有咩關係?</blockquote><br />\n就咁睇內文 八歳移民 如果係咁嘅話叫港產真係冇錯啵。分分鐘仲有香港身份證(如果仲拎住張身份證，又冇renounce中國藉，佢仲會首先係一個中國人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)。香港人身份不嬲同國藉冇關架啦<br />\n不過報紙佬拎人個岀生打飛機，又唔問下人老豆教佢嘅同外國人造嘅方法有咩唔同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n只可以計青訓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24315439420c92398bcc22166bd3afa415e2006b","tid":492672,"uid":7078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T00:25:10.000Z","msg":"一有著數就認親認戚"},{"pid":"ad14d37cdea584d88da91a5bd01fa43e69d00c9e","tid":492672,"uid":52943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T00:31:59.000Z","msg":"認親認戚認屎認屁港豬就最撚叻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efeb42a7484231ac91f7b85143f082217cfc77eb","tid":492672,"uid":52946,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T00:38:06.000Z","msg":"屌你老母一見人個樣係華人又拎著數攞威 華人DNA就係咁"},{"pid":"f13f3b547b285ed9710bf4a729541617ad8190f3","tid":492672,"uid":5637,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T00:39:47.000Z","msg":"教人哋點整空氣麵包<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53dcc5d431ac2b7a48019ec06734a4a9fb6913ee","tid":492672,"uid":112436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T00:47:20.000Z","msg":"計DNA嘅話全世界都非洲人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8439dd151782bea31622b35d1e4c8ea77d431e22","tid":492672,"uid":47268,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T00:54:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢個世界有英國麵包, 德國麵包, 法國麵包, 但就係無香港麵包</blockquote><br />\n香港麵包16號"},{"pid":"8ceb8c845a5f44dc613c59cd3792f7c07b891d37","tid":492672,"uid":5303,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T01:12:06.000Z","msg":"美國人就唔可以係香港人<img src=\"/assets/fa